WEBVTT

00:12:28.960 --> 00:12:30.160
"Šta je Tviter?"

00:12:32.640 --> 00:12:36.536
Naši zakonodavci moraju da napišu
i izglasaju mudre zakone

00:12:36.560 --> 00:12:38.456
koji su odraz savremene tehnologije

00:12:38.480 --> 00:12:41.680
i naših shvatanja slobodnog
i govora mržnje.

00:12:42.280 --> 00:12:46.816
Nedavno u Njujorku zakon
nije mogao da se primeni na počinioca

00:12:46.840 --> 00:12:49.016
jer zločini moraju biti počinjeni -

00:12:49.040 --> 00:12:50.376
čak iako su anonimni -

00:12:50.400 --> 00:12:54.856
moraju biti počinjeni
preko telefona, poštom,

00:12:54.880 --> 00:12:56.296
preko telegrafa -

00:12:56.320 --> 00:12:57.800
(Smeh)